frames.caption: A group of ducklings waddles through a sunlit meadow, surrounded by fluttering butterflies. The warm glow of the setting sun casts a golden hue over the scene, highlighting the soft feathers of the ducklings.
frames.description: The scene captures a serene moment in a natural setting, where ducklings are exploring a grassy area under the warm light of the sun. Butterflies add a whimsical touch as they flit around the ducklings.

frames.caption: A group of fluffy ducklings walk through a sunlit meadow, surrounded by fluttering butterflies. The warm glow of the setting sun casts a golden hue over the scene, creating a serene and enchanting atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene captures a tranquil moment in nature where ducklings are exploring a grassy field during sunset. Butterflies add a whimsical touch as they dance around the ducklings, enhancing the peaceful and idyllic setting.
